Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.83,0:00:27.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At the end of the century,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.30,0:00:31.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Japan's religious believers numbered 200 million,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.78,0:00:35.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,making them the majority of the total population. {??? idk how that's supposed to be possible, maybe implying they all live in some other dimension where the PR academy is?}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.36,0:00:43.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,People clung to gods and Buddhas, \Ntrying to live happy days filled with light.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.02,0:00:54.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However, where there is light, there is shadow. {??? that has to be kage, but he really makes it sound like kange = religious-fund soliciting; Buddhist preaching}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.34,0:00:57.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shadows that gave off an evil radiance \Nloomed overhead.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.63,0:01:05.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When shadows of fear and religious persecution
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.76,0:01:09.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,threatened to cover the world,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.20,0:01:13.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,one young girl stood up to them.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.41,0:01:38.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her name was...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.47,0:01:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Butt Attack Punisher Girl Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.56,0:01:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.31,0:02:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari-san, humanity needs perfect order \Nand solemn discipline; Rule through religion.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.40,0:02:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think people still need \Nthe power of love to truly be happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.95,0:02:13.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Without knowing each other's true identities, \Nthe two were drawn together.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.35,0:02:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So beautiful! It's completely turned \Ninto a winter wonderland!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.87,0:02:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been snowing for three whole days and nights!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.33,0:02:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.88,0:02:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.91,0:02:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you'll pay, Mari! Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.34,0:03:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.34,0:03:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.52,0:03:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobishima-senpai!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.83,0:03:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So we take the same route to school?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.44,0:03:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, today I just happened to have \Nsome unavoidable business.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.56,0:03:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, so it really was a total coincidence then?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.63,0:03:18.84,Thought,,0,0,0,,Coincidence?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.45,0:03:22.31,Thought,,0,0,0,,Then how do you explain all that snow \Npiled on your shoulders? {meaning he's been waiting there for hours}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.45,0:03:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels kind of destined, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.87,0:03:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.88,0:03:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting used to the academy yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.40,0:03:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Everyone's been so nice to me. {lit: everyone is a good person}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.18,0:03:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm loving PR academy!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.48,0:03:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.60,0:03:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-san isn't here.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.69,0:03:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of weirdos too, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.83,0:03:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.70,0:03:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Though there is one thing that worries me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.36,0:03:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Worries you?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.16,0:03:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Black Buddha people.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.14,0:03:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.06,0:03:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't like them.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.42,0:03:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.02,0:03:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Using violence to take away religious freedom is honestly...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,despicable!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.29,0:04:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.10,0:04:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.53,0:04:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be true, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.42,0:04:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it's still better than some shameless girl \Nexposing her ass in public.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.66,0:04:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's doomed if young girls are running around with a loincloth wedged up their butts fighting people.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.42,0:04:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's true.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.52,0:04:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's embarrassing too.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.02,0:04:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.47,0:04:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's doing it for justice.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.79,0:04:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you claim justice \Ndoesn't mean anything is justified. {meaning "if you declare you're acting in the interest of justice, doesn't imply you can do anything at all"}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.88,0:04:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.40,0:04:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What she's doing is no different \Nfrom a whore.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.55,0:04:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A w-whore?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.40,0:04:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No amount of repentance can save her. {????? ザンゲの値打ちもない女だ = "a woman for whom even repentance/confession has no value" - no clue what he means}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.15,0:05:06.87,Thought,,0,0,0,,I've never regretted my actions more than I do today.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.87,0:05:11.11,Thought,,0,0,0,,Lord, please forgive me for my shameful acts!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.16,0:05:26.76,Thought,,0,0,0,,Tobishima-senpai is right.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.76,0:05:30.31,Thought,,0,0,0,,Just because you call it justice \Ndoesn't mean you can do anything you want.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,Gautaman...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.48,Thought,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of her! {/hate it now}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.86,0:05:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind if I get in too?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.73,0:05:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, but isn't it too small for two?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.90,0:05:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.93,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Lift your leg a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.91,0:05:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.83,0:05:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A little more.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.80,0:05:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax your hips.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.82,0:05:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There, I'm in!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.83,0:06:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Having our butts touching feels kinda weird.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.18,0:06:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.02,0:06:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem down, Mari.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.70,0:06:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's not true. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.19,0:06:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar! It's written all over your face.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.19,0:06:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you bottle up too many secrets, \Nyour flower garden will overflow. {w/e she means; hanazono is slang for woman's cunny}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.41,0:06:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Flower garden?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.83,0:06:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.55,0:06:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from an old legend in the Vedas, \Nthe sacred scripture of us Hindus.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.27,0:06:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has a secret flower garden in their heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.82,0:06:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When you carry a secret you can't tell anyone, \Na flower appears there.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.86,0:06:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happens if it overflows with secrets? {/secrets become too many}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.26,0:06:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No one knows. That's why, before it overflows, \Nyou confess your secret to the person you love.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.82,0:06:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,To the person I love?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.14,0:06:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of it as them picking that flower for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.22,0:06:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.62,0:06:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Saori-chan, do you have someone you love?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.36,0:06:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.46,0:06:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... a secret!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.57,Thought,,0,0,0,,My secret...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.52,0:07:05.03,Thought,,0,0,0,,is a sad feeling that would disappear \Nif I spoke it aloud.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.72,0:07:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobishima, despite the grace period \NI gave you to find Gautaman,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.77,0:07:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,why have you made no progress?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.73,0:07:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Holiness, please grant me a little more time. {the pope}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.76,0:07:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you've become \Ndistracted by some cutesy girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.49,0:07:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's not...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.83,0:07:29.79,Thought,,0,0,0,,That sleazy vice principal ratted me out.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.79,0:07:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, she's a fine young lady, isn't she? \NNo wonder you fell for her completely.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.66,0:07:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A rare sight these days. \NIntelligent and pure-hearted.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.13,0:07:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Holiness thinks so too?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.00,0:07:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A perfect sacrifice for the National Black Buddha Mass. {supposed to say kurobutsu = black buddha but says kokubutsu for some reason, no idea why; perhaps koku = country so instead of black buddha mass it's "nationwide buddha mass"}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.95,0:07:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A sacrifice?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.64,0:07:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. To defeat Gautaman now, \Nnothing less than the ultimate brainwashed fiend,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.71,0:07:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,created through the National Mass will suffice.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.94,0:07:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A sacrifice of a beautiful, intelligent, \Ndevout young maiden.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.49,0:08:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl is perfect for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.61,0:08:04.07,Thought,,0,0,0,,My wildflower girl... must be sacrificed?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.58,0:08:23.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,Tobishima, bring that girl to me at once.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.64,0:08:25.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,We must begin the National Mass immediately.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.41,0:08:27.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.61,0:08:29.86,Thought,,0,0,0,,What will you do, Tobishima Ryo? {he asks himself}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.86,0:08:35.27,Thought,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to turn that girl \Ninto a sacrifice for the National Black Buddha Mass?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.27,0:08:39.30,Thought,,0,0,0,,But the Pope's orders are absolute.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.30,0:08:41.89,Thought,,0,0,0,,Can you not even protect the woman you love?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.89,0:08:44.45,Thought,,0,0,0,,The girl you've decided to devote your life to?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.29,0:08:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This mission is too \Nheavy a burden for Boss.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you people.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This is bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A brainwashed fiend has appeared!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.59,0:09:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! \NI never gave such an order!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.26,0:09:17.85,Note,,0,0,0,,[Tako is their surname; tako means octopus]
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.26,0:09:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mutant Takos here! {ミュータント・ターコズ = muutanto takozu - tako is octopus, so it's "takos" (plural for tako) - tako is their surname}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.85,0:09:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Amachi Mari!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.28,0:09:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll come quietly with us.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.28,0:09:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What does a Black Buddha brainwashed fiend want with Mari?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.78,0:09:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing major, really.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.12,0:09:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need her...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.24,0:09:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,As a little sacrifice.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A sacrifice?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.92,0:09:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.05,0:09:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm totally sensitive there! {lit: weak}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.09,0:09:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Hibari's in trouble! {???? hibari joosama pinchi da? not in manga}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.39,0:09:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.57,0:09:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you staring at?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.55,0:09:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! {????}{sou datta}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.54,0:09:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,On three...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.44,0:09:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.12,0:09:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.98,0:10:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.53,0:10:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! {tasukete?}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.81,0:10:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari, run for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.02,0:10:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari, transform!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.70,0:10:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Buddha!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.43,0:10:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak the incantation "Gautaman Change!"
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.00,0:10:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Gautaman Change!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.72,0:10:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,To awaken the ultimate power of Kundalini, \Nyou must open the body's seven chakras.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.60,0:10:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard vice principal went ahead... \Nand approved the operation without my permission!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.74,0:10:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobishima-senpai!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.49,0:11:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.79,0:11:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh God, I wanna die!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.19,0:11:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mari! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.43,0:11:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,From this height...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.27,0:11:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no way she could've survived... {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I done?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.02,0:11:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.65,0:11:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The orders said to bring her back alive!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.42,0:11:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna get chewed out for this!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.35,0:11:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only trying to save her...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.96,0:11:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.90,0:11:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Butt Attack Punisher Girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.11,0:11:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.31,0:11:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I already saved her!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.91,0:11:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll do it ourselves!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.56,0:11:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Take her down and earn a promotion!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.19,0:11:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go, Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.58,0:11:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Trinity Jet Stream Tako Attack! {btw this is a Gundam reference: https://youtu.be/BKqoCwYvmFk?t=43}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.58,0:11:52.55,Note,,0,0,0,,["Jet Stream Attack" = attack formation from Gundam]
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.56,0:11:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.28,0:11:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She used me as a stepping stone!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.53,0:12:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we've got you, Gautaman.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.66,0:12:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think that's an ordinary octopus.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.72,0:12:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold our ultimate weapon!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.44,0:12:23.73,Note,,0,0,0,,[chuu chuu tako kaina = traditional children's counting song: \N(chuu (4) + chuu (4) = 8 tako (octopus) kaina (arms))] {https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%81%A1%E3%82%85%E3%81%86%E3%81%A1%E3%82%85%E3%81%86%E3%81%9F%E3%81%93%E3%81%8B%E3%81%84%E3%81%AA  - I still don't understand how it's supposed to work tbh}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.44,0:12:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Octopussy Suction!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.73,0:12:25.19,Note,,0,0,0,,[chuu as SFX means "to kiss/to suck"]
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.73,0:12:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oc...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.36,0:12:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.20,0:12:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pussy...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.00,0:12:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Suc...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.68,0:12:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tion?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.57,0:12:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't pull it off! Even though Gautaman's strength \Nis several times greater than a human's!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.88,0:12:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, it's only clinging even tighter!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.21,0:12:40.44,Top,,0,0,0,,One-two... {/fight}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.44,0:12:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what nice weather...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.68,0:12:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This crystal-clear blue sky...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.06,0:12:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell! \NNow's not the time to be spacing out!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.11,0:12:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.95,0:12:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.73,0:12:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,See that? The true terror of that octopus \Nis only beginning to manifest itself!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.10,0:13:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The octopus...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.55,0:13:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,T-The octopus is getting bigger!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.02,0:13:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.75,0:13:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.51,0:13:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.05,0:13:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I must do some explanation now!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.52,0:13:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If the loincloth power, which is the source of Gautaman's ultimate weapon, Kundalini,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.14,0:13:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is forcibly drained dry, she will die!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.88,0:13:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit explaining and help her already!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.41,0:13:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A hero of justice that has \Nto rely on others is a failed hero!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.38,0:13:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Only by overcoming hardship with one's own strength \Ncan one fulfill their mission!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.36,0:13:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough, you useless god! {?????}{hitodenashi}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.61,0:13:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Buddha! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.30,0:13:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.59,0:13:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be safe.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.34,0:13:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.08,0:14:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.10,0:14:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking good, Octopussy Suction!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.90,0:14:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Suck! Suck her completely dry!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.12,0:14:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Drain every last drop of Gautaman's life force!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.95,0:14:23.51,Thought,,0,0,0,,G-Goodbye, Saori-chan...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Tobishima-senpai.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.67,0:14:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobishima-senpai, do you like sushi?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.33,0:14:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If I had to choose, I'd go with scattered sushi. {chirashi zushi = sushi rice in a box or bowl with a variety of ingredients sprinkled on top}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.41,0:14:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll make some for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.53,0:14:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait until lunchtime, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.59,0:14:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.33,0:14:47.09,Thought,,0,0,0,,Tobishima-senpai, I'm sorry I couldn't make the sushi! \NI even had everything to do it...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.25,0:14:49.49,Thought,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.99,0:14:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My bag!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.93,0:14:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the finishing blow! \NMaximum suction all at once!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.16,0:15:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What happened?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.12,0:15:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.64,0:15:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did we get her?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.30,0:15:18.63,Thought,,0,0,0,,I-Impossible! Even our strongest \Nbrainwashed fiends couldn't defeat Gautaman,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.14,0:15:21.13,Thought,,0,0,0,,and now some mutant octopus did?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.13,0:15:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.07,0:15:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.96,0:15:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell happened to Octopussy Suction?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.38,0:15:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Vinegar? It's a bottle of vinegar!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.75,0:15:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a monstrous octopus becomes nothing \Nbut pickled octopus once it absorbs vinegar!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.39,0:15:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how strong we were...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.64,0:15:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much we used our brains...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.02,0:15:43.99,Note,,0,0,0,,["tako" can also mean "clumsy" in Japanese]
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.02,0:15:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, we were only octopuses...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.65,0:15:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure is chilly today.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.38,0:15:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes you crave a nice hot octopus stew!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.34,0:15:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.75,0:15:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.44,0:16:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.38,0:16:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing warms you up \Non a cold day like a full stomach.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.06,0:16:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, gimme another helping!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.35,0:16:10.60,Thought,,0,0,0,,In the end, octopuses just weren't enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.14,0:16:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, thanks to them, I found a way \Nthat doesn't require sacrificing Mari-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.83,0:16:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If the academy students are put in danger, \NGautaman will have no choice but to appear.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.50,0:16:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your deaths were not in vain.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.70,0:16:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobishima, what happened to the sacrifice \Nfor the Black Mass, Amachi Mari?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.09,0:16:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,With all due respect, \NI no longer believe a sacrifice is necessary.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.17,0:16:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.40,0:16:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall personally destroy Gautaman \Nbefore your very eyes.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Your Holiness...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.31,0:16:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's finally gotten serious. \NThen your efforts were not wasted after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.81,0:16:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.42,0:17:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pigeon, Pigeon{hato-san}, come over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.63,0:17:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how many beans there are.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.63,0:17:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You all have to share nicely, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.30,0:17:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What should I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.42,0:17:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mari?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.16,0:17:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobishima-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.74,0:17:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,what'd he say?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.53,0:17:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He... {ko- - stutter of kondo}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.26,0:17:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.38,0:17:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He... {kon- - same}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.18,0:17:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.20,0:17:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked me to go to an amusement park with him sometime! {kondo = next time = sometime when she has time, like on the weekend}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.45,0:17:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do? \NHey, what do I do, Saori-chan?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.92,0:17:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.71,0:17:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.81,0:17:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Wait! Come with us too, Saori-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.51,0:18:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.38,0:18:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But being alone with a guy...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.68,0:18:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what a normal date is supposed to be like.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.76,0:18:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, Saori-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.39,0:18:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh... If you don't want to go, then just say no.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.81,0:18:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I don't want to...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.60,0:18:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.23,0:18:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.21,0:18:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{un}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.28,0:18:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl's hopeless.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.44,0:18:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dream is to become \Nlike Mother Teresa someday, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.69,0:18:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.72,0:18:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A missionary of love spreading love to people everywhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.67,0:18:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to become one too.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.25,0:18:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to teach people about love, then you need to know what it means to love and be loved yourself. {lit: then you need to love and be loved yourself}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.35,0:18:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be afraid of loving someone \Nand being loved in return.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.71,0:18:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,To love another person...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.48,0:18:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling what \Nthat lovestruck boss is thinking.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.36,0:18:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our chance to capture Amachi Mari \Nand earn ourselves some glory,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.94,0:19:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Brainwashed Fiend Franken Muscle! {フランケンマッスル}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.37,0:19:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,His muscle power is several times that of a gorilla. {he's talking to the viewer, not the franken muscle}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.41,0:19:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's also a good boy who always obeys me.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.63,0:19:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Though he's not so bright.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.33,0:19:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you there's no need for a sacrifice.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.31,0:19:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow some filthy monster near her!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.67,0:19:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Eek! You mustn't provoke him, Boss! \NHe's especially sensitive about insults.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.44,0:19:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It stinks! Go brush your teeth!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.87,0:19:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Franken Muscle...!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.25,0:19:47.17,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere unnecessarily.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.17,0:19:50.28,Overlap,,0,0,0,,I'll be the one to defeat Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.18,0:19:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a challenge letter!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.58,0:19:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it say?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.78,0:20:02.47,Note,,0,0,0,,[shiyuu - same word means "victory and defeat" and "male and female"; he reads it wrong to accentuate that latter meaning]
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.78,0:20:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... "To Gautaman. Today after school, at Aokigahara, \NI wish to erase the distinction between male and female."
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.47,0:20:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, it's supposed to read\N "settle things once and for all."
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.40,0:20:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,\NHuh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.04,0:20:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A challenge from the Black Buddha's boss?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.87,0:20:43.42,Thought,,0,0,0,,Has my wish become reality?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.61,0:20:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari! I'd die for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.17,0:20:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a second!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.81,0:21:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not seriously planning to go on a date \Ndressed like that, are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really? {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.85,0:21:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to dress up all cute and stylish!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.84,0:21:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What time are you meeting?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.24,0:21:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, at three.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.49,0:21:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry up and change!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.89,0:21:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you meeting?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.34,0:21:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the big chestnut tree behind the academy.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.95,0:21:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hold still.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.50,0:21:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy peasy, like that. {kinda meaningless}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.47,0:21:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, adorable.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.31,0:21:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Have fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.18,0:21:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Thanks, Saori-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.32,0:21:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really glad we became friends, Saori-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.44,0:21:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.81,0:21:55.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.24,0:21:58.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,Saori-chan, you went to all this trouble to make me look cute, and yet...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.74,0:22:00.54,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Tobishima-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.54,0:22:02.45,Thought,,0,0,0,,I might not be able to come.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.45,0:22:08.25,Thought,,0,0,0,,There's something more important than my happiness \Nas Amachi Mari... my duty as Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.55,0:22:39.62,Thought,,0,0,0,,She's late... What is Gautaman doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.93,0:22:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Butt Attack Punisher Girl...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:48.33,0:22:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.44,0:22:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:51.46,0:22:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't show any mercy.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:52.46,0:22:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I hoped!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:54.71,0:22:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself for the Gautaman Folding Fan!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:04.12,0:23:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you...! {/you are...}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:06.24,0:23:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think I'd reveal my face so easily?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.95,0:23:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already read all your moves! \NThe real battle starts now!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.07,0:23:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.20,0:23:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's strong.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.85,0:23:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's nothing like the fiends I've faced before.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.76,0:23:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.74,0:23:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Fast runner, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:48.84,0:23:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't miss next time.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.10,0:23:57.70,Thought,,0,0,0,,The ultimate power...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:57.70,0:23:59.90,Thought,,0,0,0,,If I don't unleash the Kundalini now,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:59.90,0:24:01.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,I can't win!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.16,0:24:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman Chop!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:08.79,0:24:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman Kick!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.75,0:24:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman Punch!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:16.52,0:24:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Useless. Pitifully useless. {???? kikan, kanashii made ni kikan? = not working, it's a pity but it's not working}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.83,0:24:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, our potentials are...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:24.51,0:24:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,incomparable! {on a different level}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:29.42,0:24:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope the date's going okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:32.45,0:24:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope she doesn't get dumped.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:39.45,0:24:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! My favorite photo frame...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:47.70,0:24:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Justice doesn't possess power.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:50.56,0:24:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Power itself is justice!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:52.61,0:24:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember right, \NGautaman dies if her loincloth is removed.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:57.51,0:25:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Torturing women isn't my hobby, \Nbut such is the duty of the boss of Black Buddha.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:03.13,0:25:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I must finish this. {deal the finishing blow}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:05.94,0:25:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:25:06.74,0:25:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:08.05,0:25:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,mole...!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:09.73,0:25:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The mole on the butt that appears in my dreams every night!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:13.04,0:25:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Could Gautaman's true identity be...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:21.07,0:25:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mari-chan?!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:24.07,0:25:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Pervert! Disgusting!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:27.07,0:25:31.07,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Hey... No, y-you've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:27.98,0:25:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I hate you!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:36.82,0:25:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Awaken, Gautaman! {/rise up}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:41.74,0:25:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:43.33,0:25:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:25:44.22,0:25:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gautaman Ruby's is filled with energy! {???? probably this; was "changed its color to gold" in manga}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:47.14,0:25:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Activate the Kundalini!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:49.23,0:25:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:50.39,0:25:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Special Dangerous Gautaman Crush!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:57.51,0:25:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{I-}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:58.44,0:26:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:06.02,0:26:08.77,Thought,,0,0,0,,I won, Saori-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:08.77,0:26:11.36,Thought,,0,0,0,,I prevailed, Tobishima-senpai!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:23.55,0:26:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you've gotta hurry! {hayaku shiro}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:24.25,0:26:25.50,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Wait for me! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:27.97,0:26:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:26:29.61,0:26:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The crows are cawing, \Ntime to go home! {カラスが鳴くから帰ろ}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:42.58,0:26:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Mari's having fun. {mari-tachi}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:49.46,0:26:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming... I promise I'll come!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:52.59,0:26:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me under the big chestnut tree, Mari-chan...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:59.87,0:27:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:01.45,0:27:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mari-chan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:04.26,0:27:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that my imagination?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:26.08,0:27:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what a refreshing morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:29.77,0:27:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And with the Black Buddha's boss dead, \Nwe can finally live peaceful lives now.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:34.89,0:27:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari, haven't you heard \Nfrom Tobishima-san since then?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:38.91,0:27:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{No.}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:39.63,0:27:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I waited all day under that tree. \NI wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:43.93,0:27:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The vice principal said there was a death in his family \Nand he had to rush back home.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:49.65,0:27:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's too overwhelmed to think about me right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:54.01,0:27:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. He'll come back \Nwith that cheerful smile again.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:57.35,0:27:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:27:58.66,0:28:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. I'm sure he'll come back.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:04.31,0:28:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:28:06.57,0:28:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the boss has fallen, \Nthe entire Black Buddha cult is done for!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:10.92,0:28:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Utterly destroyed!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:12.81,0:28:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not despair, Vice Principal. \NIt is too soon to give up.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:16.11,0:28:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, even Tobishima could not defeat Gautaman.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:20.13,0:28:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even creating the ultimate brainwashed fiend \Nwould not be enough to beat her.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:24.64,0:28:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what are we to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:26.29,0:28:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have one trump card.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:28.46,0:28:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself shall become \NBlack Buddha's ultimate terminator. {yes, like in cameron's film}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:33.14,0:28:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:28:34.71,0:28:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,His Holiness Pope John Dalai XIII himself?! {教皇ヨハネ・ダライニ師13世／ヨハネ・ダライニ13世T-801}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:38.56,0:28:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:28:41.77,0:28:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I live, \NBlack Buddha shall remain eternal! {Tiger Mask reference}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:41.77,0:28:47.24,Note,,0,0,0,,[Tiger Mask reference] {that's what muzu said, I have no idea exactly how it's referencing TM}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:11.43,0:29:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, shoot! I left my Veda scriptures in the classroom.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:15.87,0:29:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's go back together.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:18.18,0:29:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, it's okay. I can go alone. \NMari, you head back to the room first.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:25.16,0:29:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should've gone back with her after all...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:34.78,0:29:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:43.05,0:29:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa! Papa! Papa!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:48.05,0:29:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Mari! My dear Mari.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:52.34,0:29:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you here so suddenly?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:54.89,0:29:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd told me, I'd have come to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:57.78,0:29:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari, the thing is...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:59.34,0:30:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:30:00.43,0:30:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think we've a problem with your privates?! {omae no soko ni = your down there }
Dialogue: 10,0:30:04.18,0:30:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:30:05.74,0:30:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:07.42,0:30:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:09.06,0:30:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, Mari has lived every day \Npure, righteous, and beautiful.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:13.10,0:30:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never once neglected my prayers!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:16.03,0:30:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Place your hand firmly upon your chest...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:19.44,0:30:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, place it on your butt and think carefully!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:22.44,0:30:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:30:23.22,0:30:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing, Father?!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:26.07,0:30:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa already knows \Nthat infamous loincloth girl is you!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:30.02,0:30:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:30:30.86,0:30:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How does father know that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:34.18,0:30:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The academy newspaper you send every month.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:36.80,0:30:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even all the parents, not to mention the students, have heard the stories {毎号のように出てくるフンドシ娘の話題は父兄ならずとも知らぬ者はおらんわ}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:39.92,0:30:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of that loincloth girl appearing in every single issue!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:42.38,0:30:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:30:43.13,0:30:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:30:43.99,0:30:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:46.81,0:30:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your butt, once smooth as silk \Nand white as snow...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:51.85,0:30:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is now all rough from loincloth chafing \Nand sun damage! {ultraviolet}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:55.86,0:30:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw that photo on the front page \Nof the academy paper,
Dialogue: 10,0:31:00.23,0:31:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa could scarcely believe his eyes.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:03.81,0:31:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to believe it! \NI prayed it was just a nightmare!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:07.58,0:31:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was no mistaking it...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:09.92,0:31:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The innocent girl I raised with my own two hands... {beloved daughter}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:13.58,0:31:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,had her butt on the front page! {lit: the daughter I raised myself, Mari, it was her own butt - this order works in japanese but not in en}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:16.58,0:31:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Father!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:18.91,0:31:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't raise you so you'd end up \Nwearing such a revealing loincloth!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:23.54,0:31:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:25.81,0:31:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:31:30.48,0:31:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't understand, Mari.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:33.34,0:31:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:36.74,0:31:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you ever understand the sorrow \Nof a father whose daughter is a loincloth girl?!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:46.71,0:31:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen well. You're not allowed to transform ever again.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:49.67,0:31:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you disobey me...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:54.15,0:31:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll transfer you out immediately.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:03.60,0:32:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm late.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:11.46,0:32:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:12.78,0:32:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's odd.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:14.61,0:32:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't even turn on the lights.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:20.62,0:32:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:21.87,0:32:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Father came by.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:23.93,0:32:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy? {lit: just now}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:25.54,0:32:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:26.63,0:32:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:28.35,0:32:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But I simply can't tell you what the matter is! {lit: only this, I can't tell you}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:32.32,0:32:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Something you can't even tell your best friend?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:37.76,0:32:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:38.96,0:32:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't suffer alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:41.36,0:32:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Or am I just someone...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:43.98,0:32:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,who means nothing to you, Mari? {lit: or else, am I... to mari, just a...}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:46.05,0:32:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'll tell you!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:49.50,0:32:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're talking! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:51.00,0:32:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:51.86,0:32:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:52.97,0:32:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say it out loud, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:55.54,0:32:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:32:57.23,0:33:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I... was Gautaman! {/was}
Dialogue: 10,0:33:09.05,0:33:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Homo? {??? this scene looks the same in manga but there his line is just "!" and I don't get what it has to do with dinosaurs and homo sapiens either way; I'm guessing humu in japanese is both "Hm?" and homo [sapiens]}
Dialogue: 10,0:33:10.16,0:33:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari was Gautaman?!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:13.68,0:33:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:18.36,0:33:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for keeping it hidden from you all this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:21.18,0:33:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:22.18,0:33:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just thinking that inside your little scrawny body,
Dialogue: 10,0:33:24.85,0:33:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you were hiding such a special \Ngorgeous body and such power...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:29.06,0:33:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,just makes me admire you more, Mari!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:31.89,0:33:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But from now on, tell me everything \Nand let's fight evil together!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:36.97,0:33:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't. It's over.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:39.32,0:33:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:40.74,0:33:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Father found out. He said I must never \Ntransform into Gautaman again.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:46.73,0:33:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He said if I transform again, \Nhe'll transfer me out!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:51.10,0:33:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:52.87,0:33:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to transfer! \NI want to keep studying at this school!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:58.15,0:34:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna be separated from you!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:05.43,0:34:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly. You already took down \Nthe Black Buddha boss, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:10.84,0:34:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace has returned to the academy, and you don't have to transform into Gautaman ever again.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:16.32,0:34:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no reason for you to be transferred.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:19.40,0:34:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:21.36,0:34:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:23.73,0:34:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sleep beside you tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:27.05,0:34:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. Thanks, Saori-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:38.84,0:34:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,See, Mari? This helps you calm down, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:42.31,0:34:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:04.54,0:35:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Black Buddha brainwashed fiend!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:13.04,0:35:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But Black Buddha was destroyed \Nwhen Gautaman took down their boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:18.40,0:35:21.52,Top,,0,0,0,,The Black Buddha cult is immortal!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:21.52,0:35:24.39,Top,,0,0,0,,That boss was nothing more \Nthan this academy's branch chief.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:24.39,0:35:30.28,Top,,0,0,0,,The final fiend is the true supreme leader \Nand strongest warrior of Black Buddha!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:30.28,0:35:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the true form of Pope \NJohn Dalai XIII! Stand aside!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:35.22,0:35:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the vice principal! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:36.45,0:35:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cursed! This academy is cursed! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:40.33,0:35:42.25,Note,,0,0,0,,[Hokuto no Ken parody]
Dialogue: 10,0:35:42.92,0:35:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... What incredible power!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:46.30,0:35:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a true super-slaughtering fiend!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:48.59,0:35:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But we've got Gautaman on our side!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:52.31,0:36:11.58,Top,,0,0,0,,Gautaman! Gautaman! Gautaman! Gautaman! Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:59.37,0:36:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out already, Gautaman.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:06.73,0:36:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What should I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:08.60,0:36:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go! You absolutely mustn't transform!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:23.87,0:36:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:25.20,0:36:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Save us, Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:28.34,0:36:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Our academy's going to be torn apart!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:31.46,0:36:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Our freedom of religion will be taken away! \NWe'll be forced by brute force to submit to Black Buddha!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:38.53,0:36:41.95,Thought,,0,0,0,,What do I do? \NWhat should I do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:45.38,0:36:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord, what should I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:48.90,0:36:55.68,Top,,0,0,0,,Unless I go away, the helper shall not come to you. {not a typo, he's talking in a very simplified japanese; supposedly this is god talking in mari's mind? I assume it's buddha telling her that she should transform to make him go away? old subs turned it into this: if you don't leave, then their savior can never come. it's best that you turn away from me}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:55.68,0:37:00.16,Top,,0,0,0,,It is to your advantage that I go away.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:03.15,0:37:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mari?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:04.79,0:37:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're going to transform?!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:07.33,0:37:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go, Mari!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:08.84,0:37:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you transfer, we'll be separated!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:11.81,0:37:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We might never see each other again!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:16.97,0:37:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We promised we'd stay together forever!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:23.19,0:37:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:25.33,0:37:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're going?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:26.72,0:37:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:37:27.21,0:37:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop you anymore?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:30.53,0:37:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:32.27,0:37:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:35.87,0:37:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman, appear!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:38.33,0:37:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman Change!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:02.38,0:38:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kneel before me! \NI shall bestow Black Buddha's baptism upon you.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:07.03,0:38:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only one religion in this world!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:10.19,0:38:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Black Buddha cult!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:12.53,0:38:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see about that! {lit: I won't let you do that}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:13.99,0:38:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:15.90,0:38:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Butt Attack Punisher Girl, Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:21.57,0:38:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, it's Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:23.08,0:38:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman, she didn't... {oretachi - male form of "us"}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:24.62,0:38:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't... {atashitachi = female form of "us" - so they're both saying "she [did action] to us"; I think this might be reflected with "she's still with us... and us! and she didn't abandon us!"}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:25.90,0:38:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,abandon us!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:27.92,0:38:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've showed up, loincloth girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:30.83,0:38:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman, the rubble of this academy \Nshall make a fitting tombstone for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:36.18,0:38:40.73,Thought,,0,0,0,,Watch closely, Saori-chan. \NThis is Gautaman's final battle!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:51.44,0:38:52.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,That petite Mari... {small}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:52.96,0:38:54.58,Thought,,0,0,0,,Adorable Mari...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:54.58,0:38:57.38,Thought,,0,0,0,,I thought I was always the one protecting you.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:57.38,0:38:59.45,Thought,,0,0,0,,But I was the one being protected.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:00.00,0:39:03.50,Thought,,0,0,0,,No matter what happened, Mari \Nwas always there to help me.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:03.50,0:39:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:06.74,0:39:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last, final Gautaman Crush!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:24.02,0:39:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:30.77,0:39:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A robot?!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:12.58,0:40:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{???}
Dialogue: 10,0:40:21.42,0:40:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, our Gautaman! {bokura = male form of our}\NYou're strong, everyone's Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:27.36,0:40:32.04,Thought,,0,0,0,,I won. But I can barely stand now...
Dialogue: 10,0:40:43.13,0:40:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Pft... {??? think it's supposed to be the sfx of him running out of steam? clanking?}
Dialogue: 10,0:40:44.18,0:40:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Grr! What do you mean, "pft"? {what the robot just said}
Dialogue: 10,0:40:46.46,0:40:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't screw with us, you damn idiot! {???? idk why this is here, maybe because "tako" is also "idiot"}
Dialogue: 10,0:40:49.39,0:40:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all gang up on him!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:51.86,0:40:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{kono kono}
Dialogue: 10,0:40:52.50,0:40:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't cut there!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:55.90,0:40:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop... {yamero?}
Dialogue: 10,0:40:58.56,0:41:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Say no to school violence...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:11.39,0:41:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, Mari.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:15.16,0:41:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-chan...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:46.39,0:41:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-chan, I'll write you letters.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:53.04,0:41:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll write lots and lots of them!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:02.06,0:42:05.05,Thought,,0,0,0,,I have to say it. I have to say it properly! {meaning not hold it back forever}
Dialogue: 10,0:42:11.95,0:42:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Mari.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:13.46,0:42:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:14.75,0:42:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll always be friends forever, got it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:20.15,0:42:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good... {bye}
Dialogue: 10,0:42:32.25,0:42:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't bring myself to say goodbye to you, Mari!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:35.83,0:42:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, Saori-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:40.31,0:42:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:41.74,0:42:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:47.02,0:42:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Mari!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:50.34,0:42:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've loved you since the day we met! {forever and ever - but in the past tense}
Dialogue: 10,0:43:00.04,0:43:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:03.24,0:43:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back anytime!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:05.77,0:43:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And until then, no matter what happens \Nto the academy, I'll protect it!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:10.34,0:43:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a promise, Mari!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:13.34,0:43:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Saori-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:17.63,0:43:20.21,Thought,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, my beloved.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:21.72,0:43:25.05,Thought,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Tobishima-senpai.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:40.72,0:43:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Auxiliary power circuit activated.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:45.21,0:43:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Auxiliary power circuit activated.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:35.67,0:44:42.38,Song,,0,0,0,,{the same song as in the first ova, still no trace of lyrics} Were you serious? Was it not a lie?
Dialogue: 10,0:44:42.38,0:44:48.27,Song,,0,0,0,,Even now, there's no way you're waiting for me
Dialogue: 10,0:44:51.31,0:44:58.58,Song,,0,0,0,,The eyes you showed me every time we met,
Dialogue: 10,0:44:58.58,0:45:04.50,Song,,0,0,0,,I really can't forget them
Dialogue: 10,0:45:05.74,0:45:14.66,Song,,0,0,0,,When my longing to see you starts to drift far away,
Dialogue: 10,0:45:14.66,0:45:23.09,Song,,0,0,0,,I dream of that classroom from that day, and of you looking at me
Dialogue: 10,0:45:23.09,0:45:23.96,Song,,0,0,0,,I need {???????? maybe "only" but all the others are clearly "ai nii" maybe it's ai ni = in love}
Dialogue: 10,0:45:23.96,0:45:28.51,Song,,0,0,0,,If it's fate, someday {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:45:31.29,0:45:39.05,Song,,0,0,0,,Someday, with those same eyes, take me anywhere with you
Dialogue: 10,0:45:39.05,0:45:39.84,Song,,0,0,0,,I need {same}
Dialogue: 10,0:45:39.84,0:45:44.65,Song,,0,0,0,,Something I couldn't even say to a friend
Dialogue: 10,0:45:46.76,0:45:56.59,Song,,0,0,0,,Someday, it's okay to paint it in sunset colors, \Nthis first love I protected too much
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.59,0:45:59.59,Song,,0,0,0,,
